{"commentv2": 1, "number": 28, "id": 1881763, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "1131778", "body": "is this boss made up by Blizzard or really exists in WC3 lore?", "date": "2013-07-28T18:18:09-05:00", "rating": -10, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Lei Shen is the first Mogu emperor and was not present in WC3", "creationdate": "2013-07-29T20:24:54-05:00", "id": 681388, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1881763, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "NadiaEF", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "A lot of bosses that are last in raids are in WC3 lore, like Illidan and the Lich King.", "creationdate": "2013-07-31T18:51:41-05:00", "id": 681824, "rating": -1, "commentid": 1881763, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Majestic36", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "All of the lore is made up by Blizzard :/", "creationdate": "2013-09-19T15:20:09-05:00", "id": 694632, "rating": 4, "commentid": 1881763, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Bronius", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "why do you assume all of the bosses have to be part of warcraft 3 or else can't be a boss? Ragnaros was a vanilla boss and wasn't. Deathwing was in 2 not 3 and Garrosh wasn't in any of of the RTS games either, nor were any of the old god bosses, or Alak'ir from Throne of 4 winds. Just because it's an \"end\" boss doesn't mean it had to have come from Warcraft 3. Also, it is highly erroneous calling it \"warcraft 3\" lore as 3 falls into the totality of Warcraft lore and while some lore gets added after the more noted lore cause it's stuff that happened elsewhere while stuff like WC3 happened.", "creationdate": "2013-09-27T09:52:58-05:00", "id": 696813, "rating": 4, "commentid": 1881763, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "redfinale", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
