{"commentv2": 1, "number": 35, "id": 2268670, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "yzq85", "body": "Paul Nakauchi is the voice behind Lei Shen, but given how he pitched his voice to resemble Christopher Lee's, it's hard not to make that mistake.\r\n\r\nNakauchi is also in Reaper of Souls as Malthael.", "date": "2015-10-26T10:35:33-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
