{"commentv2": 1, "number": 58, "id": 3210533, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Seldomane", "body": "IF YOU ARE NOT GETTING CUTESCENE AFTER LEI SHEN / CAN'T FIND RA-DEN:\n\nWhen you enter the instance, the difficulty you select will remain until approximately Iron Qon.  Either before or after Iron Qon, the difficulty AUTOMATICALLY changed from Heroic to Normal.  You must change it back to Heroic & leave the instance, and re-enter, in order to face Lei Shen and Ra-Den.\n\nFirst attempt:  I went into ToT on one toon this morning, I set it to Heroic 25-man (solo as 120 of course) and entered.  When I defeated Lei Shen, I received no cutscene and couldn't fight Ra-Den.  I checked the difficulty and it was set to Normal.  This pissed me off as I knew I set it to Heroic before entering.\n\nSecond attempt:  I went in a second time on another 120 toon, made damn sure I was set to heroic 25-man.  Right before I faced Lei Shen I checked difficulty and again it was set to Normal.  So I changed it to Heroic, the prompt came up to \"accept\" being in an instance in progress, which I accepted of course.  I continued to Lei Shen to find out that he wasn't there!  Nothing.  Just an empty platform.  \n\nThird attempt:  Third alt... same situation, but I constantly checked the difficulty because I knew it changed at some point.  It seemed to changed after defeating Iron Qon to Normal.  so I immediately changed it back and continued to Lei Shen, who of course WASN'T THERE AGAIN.  \n\nFourth attempt:  Finally got it done... I did the same steps as above, but after defeating Iron Qon, I changed difficulty from normal to heroic and I left the raid completely (porting back with toy), and then ran back to instance and ran all the way back to where I was, and Lei Shen was there!  After beating him the cutscene happened and I was able to fight Ra-Den.\n\nSO!...  If you want to complete the instance and beat Ra-Den:  After defeating Iron Qon you have to leave the dungeon and change it difficulty back to heroic, and then go back in and finish Lei Shen and Ra-Den.  That's the ONLY way I've been able to complete it.", "date": "2020-06-03T21:19:07-05:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Can't upvote this enough. Just happened to my wife and I this morning. Will have to try next raid reset. Thank you very much for this.", "creationdate": "2020-07-26T10:47:13-05:00", "id": 1381186, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3210533, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Thommas", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "What toy? Ports yu to where?", "creationdate": "2020-10-14T23:57:21-05:00", "id": 1396728, "rating": 0, "commentid": 3210533, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "fiercefiona", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2020-06-03T21:31:50-05:00", 4, "Seldomane"]}